Open Source For You - September 2014  IN

108 Pages | True PDF | English | 11 MB 

The magazine carries tech articles on Linux and open source for newbies, administrators, developers and fans of open source. Its main objective, however, is to help organisations enhance their return on investment (RoI) by deploying Linux (or open source) solutions.
